These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Flower   | tulip | daffodil | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, tea
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Beverage   | juice | tea | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Sport   | sailing | ice-hockey | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, may, february
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | december | may | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Cigar   | prince | aristoff | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
City: london, colone, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| City   | london | colone | venice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
