.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
House: ranch-style, victorian, cape-cod
1. the victorian house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
2. the cape-cod house is between the victorian house and the ranch-style house##2
3. the victorian house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| House   | victorian | cape-cod | ranch-style |

