.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | drama | thriller |

 